## API surface

| Route              | Description                                       |
|--------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| `GET /api/v1/health` | Liveness (delegates to Spring Actuator)         |
| `GET /api/v1/items`  | List all items                                  |
| `POST /api/v1/items` | Create item (JSON body)                         |
| `GET /api/v1/items/{id}` | Fetch by id                                 |
| `DELETE /api/v1/items/{id}` | Delete by id                             |

